.TH YOCTOFETCH 1
.SH NAME
.B yoctofetch
— system fetch tool
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B yoctofetch
.SH DESCRIPTION
Fast system fetch tool for Linux with a low footprint.

Similar to neofetch, fastfetch etc. with comparably less features but really
high performance and a tiny binary size.

.SH FILES
.PP
/etc/yoctofetch.conf
.RS 4
System wide configuration file.
Will be loaded if no user configuration file is found.
Described in detail in yoctofetch_config(5).
.RE

.PP
~/.config/yoctofetch/yoctofetch.conf
.RS 4
User configuration file. Described in detail in yoctofetch_config(5).
.RE

.SH SEE ALSO
yoctofetch_config(5)

.SH AUTHOR
Written by Luca Kredel

.SH BUGS
None, of course. /s

